00:20:26.192 --> 00:20:27.692
(WIND GUSTING)

271
00:20:46.212 --> 00:20:48.880
Mushu, awaken.

272
00:20:50.383 --> 00:20:51.883
(CLANKING)

273
00:20:54.887 --> 00:20:57.389
I live!

274
00:20:58.599 --> 00:21:01.768
So tell me what mortal needs
my protection, great ancestor.


275
00:21:01.852 --> 00:21:04.312
-You just say the word and I'm there.
-Mushu. . .


276
00:21:04.397 --> 00:21:05.355
And let me say somethin'.

277
00:21:05.439 --> 00:21:08.149
Anybody who's foolish enough
to threaten our family,


278
00:21:08.234 --> 00:21:09.776
vengeance will be mine!

279
00:21:10.653 --> 00:21:11.945
(GROWLING)

280
00:21:12.238 --> 00:21:13.822
Mushu !

281
00:21:13.906 --> 00:21:16.658
These are the family guardians.

282
00:21:16.742 --> 00:21:20.245
-They. . .
-Protect the family.


283
00:21:20.329 --> 00:21:23.999
And you, O demoted one?

284
00:21:24.083 --> 00:21:26.876
I ring the gong.

285
00:21:26.961 --> 00:21:31.256
That's right.
Now, wake up the ancestors.


286
00:21:31.340 --> 00:21:32.424
(DISGUSTED SIGH)

287
00:21:32.508 --> 00:21:35.176
One family reunion comin' right up.

288
00:21:35.261 --> 00:21:37.679
Okay, people, people, look alive.
Let's go. Come on. Get up.


289
00:21:37.763 --> 00:21:39.305
Let's move it. 
Rise and shine.

290
00:21:39.390 --> 00:21:42.517
Y'all way past the beauty sleep thing,
trust me.


291
00:21:43.644 --> 00:21:45.437
(ANCESTORS MUTTERING)

292
00:21:46.439 --> 00:21:51.317
I knew it. I knew it. That Mulan was
a troublemaker from the start!


293
00:21:51.402 --> 00:21:53.945
Don't look at me.
She gets it from your side of the family.


294
00:21:54.030 --> 00:21:56.489
She's just trying to help her father.

295
00:21:56.574 --> 00:21:59.242
But if she's discovered,
Fa Zhou will be forever shamed.


296
00:21:59.326 --> 00:22:02.537
Dishonor will come to the family.
Traditional values will disintegrate.


297
00:22:02.621 --> 00:22:04.372
Not to mention, they'll lose the farm.

298
00:22:04.457 --> 00:22:08.293
My children never caused such trouble.
They all became acupuncturists.


299
00:22:08.377 --> 00:22:11.337
-We can't all be acupuncturists.
-OLDER LADY: No!


300
00:22:11.422 --> 00:22:14.632
Your great-granddaughter
had to be a cross-dresser!


301
00:22:14.759 --> 00:22:16.468
(ANCESTORS ARGUING)

302
00:22:17.219 --> 00:22:19.137
Let a guardian bring her back.

303
00:22:19.221 --> 00:22:21.181
Yes, awaken the most cunning.

304
00:22:21.265 --> 00:22:23.183
No. The swiftest.

305
00:22:23.267 --> 00:22:25.894
-No. Send the wisest.
-GREAT ANCESTOR: Silence!


306
00:22:25.978 --> 00:22:28.938
We must send the most powerful of all.

307
00:22:29.023 --> 00:22:30.231
(MUSHU LAUGHING)

308
00:22:30.316 --> 00:22:34.277
Okay, okay, I get the drift. I'll go.

309
00:22:34.445 --> 00:22:35.945
(ALL LAUGHING)

310
00:22:36.864 --> 00:22:39.157
Y'all don't think I can do it.
Watch this here.


311
00:22:39.241 --> 00:22:40.325
(INHALES)

312
00:22:40.826 --> 00:22:42.994
Jump back. I'm pretty hot, huh?

313
00:22:43.079 --> 00:22:45.288
Don't make me have to singe nobody
to prove no point.


314
00:22:45.372 --> 00:22:48.083
You had your chance
to protect the Fa family.


315
00:22:48.167 --> 00:22:50.835
Your misguidance led
Fa Deng to disaster.


316
00:22:50.920 --> 00:22:54.130
-Yeah, thanks a lot.
-And your point is?


317
00:22:54.215 --> 00:22:59.552
The point is we will be sending
a real dragon to retrieve Mulan.


318
00:22:59.637 --> 00:23:01.888
What. . . What. . . 
I'm a real dragon !

319
00:23:01.972 --> 00:23:07.685
You are not worthy of this spot.
Now, awaken the Great Stone Dragon.


320
00:23:09.021 --> 00:23:12.148
So you'll get back to me
on the job thing?


321
00:23:12.233 --> 00:23:13.858
(DISGUSTED SIGH)

322
00:23:14.527 --> 00:23:17.195
Just one chance,
is that too much to ask?


323
00:23:17.279 --> 00:23:20.448
I mean, it's not like it'd kill ya.

324
00:23:20.533 --> 00:23:23.910
Yo, Rocky, wake up!
Ya gotta go fetch Mulan !


325
00:23:27.665 --> 00:23:30.166
Come on, boy! Go
get her! Go on !

326
00:23:30.251 --> 00:23:32.460
(WHISTLES) Come on.

327
00:23:33.129 --> 00:23:34.462
(GONG BANGING)

328
00:23:35.965 --> 00:23:37.298
(GROWLING)

329
00:23:40.553 --> 00:23:42.470
Hello?

330
00:23:42.555 --> 00:23:46.975
Hello!

331
00:23:47.059 --> 00:23:48.935
Uh-oh.

332
00:23:56.110 --> 00:23:57.735
Uh, Stony?

333
00:23:58.362 --> 00:24:01.489
Stony? Oh, man, they're gonna kill me.

334
00:24:01.574 --> 00:24:03.992
GREAT ANCESTOR:
Great Stone Dragon,


335
00:24:04.076 --> 00:24:06.828
have you awakened?

336
00:24:07.705 --> 00:24:10.415
MUSHU: Uh, uh. . . Yes, 
I just woke up.

337
00:24:10.499 --> 00:24:14.252
I'm. . . I'm the Great Stone Dragon.
Good morning.


338
00:24:14.336 --> 00:24:16.880
I will go forth and fetch Mulan.

339
00:24:16.964 --> 00:24:20.258
Did I mention that
I was the Great Stone Dragon?


340
00:24:20.384 --> 00:24:23.344
Go! The fate of the Fa family

341
00:24:23.429 --> 00:24:26.014
rests in your claws.

342
00:24:26.098 --> 00:24:29.559
Don't even worry about it.
I will not lose face.


343
00:24:29.643 --> 00:24:31.269
(SCREAMING AND GRUNTING)

344
00:24:31.937 --> 00:24:33.229
(MOANING)

345
00:24:33.439 --> 00:24:34.731
My elbow!

346
00:24:34.815 --> 00:24:37.609
(GROANING) I know I twisted somethin'.

347
00:24:37.693 --> 00:24:39.235
(GRUNTING)

348
00:24:39.612 --> 00:24:41.738
That's just great. Now what?

349
00:24:41.822 --> 00:24:42.822
I'm doomed,

350
00:24:42.907 --> 00:24:46.618
and all 'cause Miss Man decides
to take her little drag show on the road.


351
00:24:48.078 --> 00:24:49.412
(CHIRPS)

352
00:24:49.538 --> 00:24:50.705
(SQUEAKING)

353
00:24:50.789 --> 00:24:53.416
Go get her? What's the matter with you?

354
00:24:53.500 --> 00:24:55.376
After this Great Stone,
Humpty Dumpty mess,


355
00:24:55.461 --> 00:24:58.546
I'd have to bring her home
with a medal to get back in the temple.


356
00:24:58.631 --> 00:25:00.882
(GASPS) Wait a minute. That's it!

357
00:25:00.966 --> 00:25:04.135
I make Mulan a war hero, and they'll be
begging me to come back to work.


358
00:25:04.220 --> 00:25:07.096
That's the master plan.
Oh, you done it now, man.


359
00:25:07.264 --> 00:25:08.556
(CHIRPS)

360
00:25:09.266 --> 00:25:10.391
(CRICKET CHIRPING)

361
00:25:10.476 --> 00:25:12.477
What makes you think you're comin'?

362
00:25:12.561 --> 00:25:14.062
(CHIRPING)

363
00:25:14.230 --> 00:25:15.730
You're lucky? (CHUCKLING)

364
00:25:16.440 --> 00:25:18.733
-Do I look like a sucker to you?
-(CHIRPS)


365
00:25:18.859 --> 00:25:20.235
What you mean, a loser?

366
00:25:20.319 --> 00:25:23.029
How 'bout I pop one of your antennas off,
throw it across the yard?


367
00:25:23.113 --> 00:25:25.406
-Then who's the loser, me or you?
-(CHIRPS)


368
00:25:28.661 --> 00:25:30.245
(SCREECHING)

369
00:25:41.340 --> 00:25:42.715
(WHINNYING)

370
00:25:55.521 --> 00:25:56.980
(BOTH GROAN)

371
00:25:57.982 --> 00:26:00.733
Imperial scouts.

372
00:26:10.703 --> 00:26:12.245
Shan
-Yu.

373
00:26:13.914 --> 00:26:15.290
(SCREECHES)

374
00:26:16.959 --> 00:26:20.878
Nice work, gentlemen.
You found the Hun army.


375
00:26:21.046 --> 00:26:22.547
(HUNS LAUGHING)

376
00:26:23.465 --> 00:26:25.466
The Emperor will stop you.

377
00:26:25.551 --> 00:26:29.053
Stop me? He invited me.

378
00:26:29.555 --> 00:26:30.805
-(GRUNTS)
-(GROANS)


379
00:26:30.889 --> 00:26:34.600
By building his wall,
he challenged my strength.


380
00:26:34.685 --> 00:26:36.936
Well, I'm here to play his game.

381
00:26:38.939 --> 00:26:43.943
Go! Tell your Emperor
to send his strongest armies.


382
00:26:44.028 --> 00:26:45.278
I'm ready.

383
00:26:49.199 --> 00:26:51.826
How many men does it take
to deliver a message?


384
00:26:51.910 --> 00:26:54.537
One.

385
00:26:58.417 --> 00:27:00.752
Okay, okay, how about this?

386
00:27:00.919 --> 00:27:01.919
(COUGHS)

387
00:27:02.004 --> 00:27:03.212
(IN DEEP VOICE) Excuse me.

388
00:27:03.297 --> 00:27:05.340
Where do I sign in?

389
00:27:05.424 --> 00:27:09.594
I see you have a sword. 
I have one, too.

390
00:27:09.678 --> 00:27:12.096
They're very manly and tough.

391
00:27:12.973 --> 00:27:14.349
(NEIGHING)

392
00:27:15.726 --> 00:27:17.935
I'm working on it!

393
00:27:18.103 --> 00:27:19.228
(SIGHS)

394
00:27:19.396 --> 00:27:21.064
Who am I fooling?

395
00:27:21.148 --> 00:27:24.275
It's going to take a miracle
to get me into the army.


396
00:27:24.360 --> 00:27:27.278
Did I hear someone ask for a miracle?

397
00:27:27.363 --> 00:27:29.864
-Let me hear you say "Aaah"!
-Aaah !


398
00:27:29.948 --> 00:27:32.075
-That's close enough.
-A ghost.


399
00:27:32.159 --> 00:27:35.620
Get ready, Mulan.
Your serpentine salvation is at hand !


400
00:27:35.704 --> 00:27:38.706
For I have been sent by your ancestors

401
00:27:38.791 --> 00:27:41.459
to guide you through your masquerade.

402
00:27:41.543 --> 00:27:43.628
Come on. If you're gonna stay,
you're gonna work.


403
00:27:43.712 --> 00:27:48.174
So heed my word ! 'Cause if
the army finds out you're a girl,


404
00:27:48.258 --> 00:27:51.469
the penalty is death !

405
00:27:51.553 --> 00:27:55.598
-Who are you?
-Who am I? Who am I?


406
00:27:55.682 --> 00:27:59.102
I am the guardian of lost souls.

407
00:27:59.186 --> 00:28:01.813
I am the powerful, the pleasurable,

408
00:28:01.897 --> 00:28:04.357
the indestructible Mushu.

409
00:28:05.818 --> 00:28:07.402
(CHUCKLES) Pretty hot, huh?

410
00:28:10.406 --> 00:28:11.656
(GROANS)

411
00:28:13.909 --> 00:28:17.495
Uh, my ancestors sent
a little lizard to help me?


412
00:28:17.663 --> 00:28:20.832
Hey, dragon, dragon, not lizard.

413
00:28:20.916 --> 00:28:23.543
I don't do that tongue thing.

414
00:28:23.627 --> 00:28:25.545
You're. . .

415
00:28:25.629 --> 00:28:27.880
Intimidating? Awe-inspiring?

416
00:28:27.965 --> 00:28:29.424
-Tiny.
-Of course.


417
00:28:29.508 --> 00:28:31.259
I'm travel size for your convenience.

418
00:28:31.343 --> 00:28:35.138
If I was my real size,
your cow here would die of fright.


419
00:28:35.222 --> 00:28:39.600
Down, Bessie. My powers are
beyond your mortal imagination.


420
00:28:39.685 --> 00:28:43.521
For instance, my eyes can see
straight through your armor.


421
00:28:43.605 --> 00:28:44.689
Oh !

422
00:28:45.607 --> 00:28:49.110
All right, that's it! Dishonor!
Dishonor on your whole family.


423
00:28:49.194 --> 00:28:52.947
Make a note of this. Dishonor on you,
dishonor on your cow. . .


424
00:28:53.031 --> 00:28:56.117
Stop. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

425
00:28:56.201 --> 00:28:58.619
I'm just nervous.
I've never done this before.


426
00:28:58.704 --> 00:29:02.457
Then you're gonna have to trust me.
And don't you slap me no more.


427
00:29:02.541 --> 00:29:04.667
We clear on that? All right.

428
00:29:04.751 --> 00:29:06.627
Okey-dokey.
Let's get this show on the road !


429
00:29:06.712 --> 00:29:07.795
Cri
-Kee, get the bags.

430
00:29:07.880 --> 00:29:10.298
-Let's move it, Heifer.
-(SNORTS)


431
00:29:10.883 --> 00:29:12.550
(MEN CHATTERING)

432
00:29:14.052 --> 00:29:16.762
Okay, this is it.
Time to show 'em your man walk.


433
00:29:16.847 --> 00:29:21.142
Shoulders back, chest high,
feet apart, head up and strut.


434
00:29:21.226 --> 00:29:25.730
Two, three. . . Break it down.
Hup, two, three. And work it!


435
00:29:28.358 --> 00:29:31.110
-Beautiful, isn't he?
-They're disgusting.


436
00:29:31.195 --> 00:29:32.528
No, they're men.

437
00:29:32.613 --> 00:29:34.780
Now, you gonna have to act
just like them, so pay attention.


438
00:29:34.865 --> 00:29:39.202
Look. This tattoo will protect me
from harm.


439
00:29:39.286 --> 00:29:40.495
Hmm.

440
00:29:41.371 --> 00:29:43.039
-(GROANS)
-(LAUGHING)


441
00:29:43.415 --> 00:29:45.458
I hope you can get your money back.

442
00:29:45.542 --> 00:29:47.543
I don't think I can do this.

443
00:29:47.628 --> 00:29:50.338
It's all attitude.
Be tough, like this guy here.


444
00:29:50.422 --> 00:29:53.591
(SNORTING) What are you lookin' at?

445
00:29:53.675 --> 00:29:56.302
Punch him. It's how men say hello.

446
00:29:57.930 --> 00:30:00.389
Yao, you've made a friend.

447
00:30:00.474 --> 00:30:02.934
Good. Now slap him on the behind.
They like that.


448
00:30:03.727 --> 00:30:05.144
Whoa-ho-ho!

449
00:30:05.270 --> 00:30:09.065
I'm gonna hit you so hard,
it'll make your ancestors dizzy.


450
00:30:09.149 --> 00:30:12.193
Yao, relax and chant with me.

451
00:30:12.361 --> 00:30:13.861
(GROWLING)

452
00:30:13.946 --> 00:30:15.446
(CHANTING)

453
00:30:18.742 --> 00:30:20.201
(YAO CHANTING)

454
00:30:21.328 --> 00:30:23.704
-(MUTTERING GIBBERISH)
-Feel better?


455
00:30:23.789 --> 00:30:27.542
Yeah. Ah, you ain't worth my time.

456
00:30:27.626 --> 00:30:29.710
-Chicken boy.
-(SCREAMING) Chicken boy?


457
00:30:29.795 --> 00:30:32.088
Say that to my face, ya limp noodle!

458
00:30:32.631 --> 00:30:33.965
(GROWLS)

459
00:30:35.676 --> 00:30:38.594
Oh ! Sorry, Ling.

460
00:30:38.929 --> 00:30:39.929
Hey!

461
00:30:41.223 --> 00:30:43.599
You're dead !

462
00:30:47.813 --> 00:30:49.105
Oh, there he goes!

463
00:30:52.276 --> 00:30:54.652
-(CLATTERING)
-(CHICKENS CLUCKING)


464
00:31:00.659 --> 00:31:01.993
(GRUNTING)

465
00:31:03.161 --> 00:31:04.912
(MEN GROANING)

466
00:31:07.499 --> 00:31:09.917
MULAN: Guys.

467
00:31:10.002 --> 00:31:13.254
The Huns have struck here,
here and here.


468
00:31:13.338 --> 00:31:16.257
I will take the main troops
up to the Tung Shao Pass,


469
00:31:16.341 --> 00:31:20.011
and stop Shan-Yu
before he destroys this village.


470
00:31:20.095 --> 00:31:22.430
Excellent strategy, sir.

471
00:31:22.514 --> 00:31:25.391
I do love surprises. (CHUCKLING)

472
00:31:26.727 --> 00:31:28.978
You will stay and train the new recruits.

473
00:31:29.062 --> 00:31:31.814
When Chi Fu believes you're ready,

474
00:31:31.898 --> 00:31:33.899
you will join us, Captain.

475
00:31:33.984 --> 00:31:35.901
Captain?

476
00:31:35.986 --> 00:31:40.072
(GASPS) This is an enormous
responsibility, General.


477
00:31:40.157 --> 00:31:42.074
Perhaps a soldier with more experience.

478
00:31:42.159 --> 00:31:46.537
Number one in his class, extensive
knowledge of training techniques,


479
00:31:46.622 --> 00:31:49.165
and impressive military lineage.

480
00:31:49.249 --> 00:31:52.001
I believe Li Shang will do
an excellent job.


481
00:31:52.085 --> 00:31:56.464
Oh, I will. I won't let you down.
This is. . . I mean. . . (CLEARS THROAT)


482
00:31:56.548 --> 00:31:59.467
-Yes, sir.
-Very good, then.


483
00:31:59.551 --> 00:32:03.054
We'll toast China's victory
at the Imperial City.


484
00:32:03.138 --> 00:32:06.349
I'll expect a full report in three weeks.

485
00:32:06.433 --> 00:32:09.727
And I won't leave anything out.

486
00:32:12.189 --> 00:32:14.482
Captain Li Shang.

487
00:32:14.566 --> 00:32:16.067
Hmm. (CHUCKLES)

488
00:32:16.568 --> 00:32:19.445
Leader of China's finest troops.

489
00:32:19.529 --> 00:32:22.865
No. The greatest troops of all time.

490
00:32:22.949 --> 00:32:24.450
(MEN YELLING)

491
00:32:28.038 --> 00:32:29.330
(MOANING)

492
00:32:31.917 --> 00:32:34.251
Most impressive.

493
00:32:37.297 --> 00:32:40.049
-(WHINNIES)
-Good luck, Captain !


494
00:32:40.175 --> 00:32:41.258
(URGES HORSE)

495
00:32:47.140 --> 00:32:50.434
Good luck, Father.

496
00:32:54.648 --> 00:32:55.898
(MEN YELLING)

497
00:32:56.316 --> 00:32:57.650
(FIGHTING CONTINUES)

498
00:32:57.734 --> 00:33:00.361
Day one.

499
00:33:01.822 --> 00:33:03.948
Soldiers!

500
00:33:04.950 --> 00:33:06.867
TOGETHER: He started it!

501
00:33:13.709 --> 00:33:16.377
I don't need anyone
causing trouble in my camp.


502
00:33:16.461 --> 00:33:18.295
(SOFTLY) Sorry.

503
00:33:18.380 --> 00:33:19.463
Uh. . . (CLEARS THROAT)

504
00:33:19.548 --> 00:33:22.299
(IN DEEP VOICE)
I mean, sorry you had to see that.


505
00:33:22.384 --> 00:33:25.636
But you know how it is
when you get those manly urges


506
00:33:25.721 --> 00:33:27.388
and you just gotta kill somethin',

507
00:33:27.472 --> 00:33:31.058
(GROANS) fix things, cook outdoors. . .

508
00:33:31.143 --> 00:33:34.812
-What's your name?
-(STAMMERING)


509
00:33:34.896 --> 00:33:38.566
Your commanding officer
just asked you a question.


510
00:33:38.650 --> 00:33:42.945
I've got a name.
And it's a boy's name, too.


511
00:33:43.029 --> 00:33:45.823
-Ling. How 'bout Ling?
-His name is Ling.


512
00:33:45.907 --> 00:33:48.909
I didn't ask for his name.
I asked for yours!


513
00:33:48.994 --> 00:33:51.746
-Try, uh, uh, ah, Chu.
-Ah Chu.


514
