780
00:49:03.949 --> 00:49:06.660
Who always speaks her mind?

781
00:49:06.744 --> 00:49:07.786
TOGETHER: Nah !

782
00:49:07.870 --> 00:49:10.580
My manly ways and turn of phrase

783
00:49:10.665 --> 00:49:13.124
Are sure to thriII her

784
