787
00:49:28.683 --> 00:49:31.685
MEN:
But when we come home in victory


788
00:49:31.769 --> 00:49:34.688
They'll line up at the door

789
00:49:34.772 --> 00:49:39.901
-What do we want?
-A girl worth fighting for


790
00:49:39.985 --> 00:49:44.155
-Wish that I had
-A girl worth fighting for


791
00:49:45.658 --> 00:49:46.700
(WHISTLING)

792
00:49:46.784 --> 00:49:48.451
A girl worth fighting...

793
00:49:57.795 --> 00:49:59.129
(CLANKING)

794
00:50:17.440 --> 00:50:19.357
Search for survivors.

795
00:50:26.866 --> 00:50:28.742
-(CREAKING)
-(WHINNIES)


796
00:50:43.507 --> 00:50:45.216
(HORSE NICKERS)

797
00:50:48.804 --> 00:50:53.600
I don't understand.
My father should've been here.


798
00:50:53.684 --> 00:50:55.643
Captain !

799
00:51:07.323 --> 00:51:09.199
The General.

800
00:51:49.406 --> 00:51:51.366
I'm sorry.

801
00:52:02.503 --> 00:52:03.878
(NICKERS)

802
00:52:10.386 --> 00:52:12.929
The Huns are moving quickly.

803
00:52:13.013 --> 00:52:16.683
We'll make better time to the Imperial
City through the Tung Shao Pass.


804
00:52:16.767 --> 00:52:19.644
We're the only hope
for the Emperor now.


805
00:52:19.728 --> 00:52:21.729
Move out!

806
00:52:43.669 --> 00:52:45.211
(BELL CLANKING)

807
00:53:04.189 --> 00:53:05.648
(ALL GASPING)

808
00:53:09.695 --> 00:53:11.070
(CHIRPING)

809
00:53:13.240 --> 00:53:15.199
-What happened?
-Uh. . .


810
00:53:15.284 --> 00:53:17.368
You just gave away our position !
Now we're. . .


811
00:53:17.828 --> 00:53:19.162
(GRUNTING)

812
00:53:19.747 --> 00:53:21.289
(BATTLE CRIES)

813
00:53:22.166 --> 00:53:24.459
Get out of range!

814
00:53:24.668 --> 00:53:26.044
(SCREAMING)

815
00:53:32.843 --> 00:53:34.010
Aah !

816
00:53:37.389 --> 00:53:38.431
(WHINNIES)

817
00:53:38.515 --> 00:53:40.058
Save the cannons!

818
00:53:40.142 --> 00:53:45.355
-(ALL SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY)
-Come on ! Empty it! Empty it!


819
00:53:56.867 --> 00:53:58.493
MUSHU: Hey!

820
00:54:00.537 --> 00:54:03.498
Oh, sure. Save the horse.

821
00:54:08.963 --> 00:54:10.213
Fire!

822
00:54:12.883 --> 00:54:14.342
(SCREAMING)

823
00:54:15.636 --> 00:54:16.719
(WHIMPERING)

824
00:54:20.849 --> 00:54:22.725
Fire!

825
00:54:29.024 --> 00:54:30.608
Hold the last cannon.

826
00:54:42.329 --> 00:54:43.746
(WHINNIES)

827
00:54:53.424 --> 00:54:54.924
(BATTLE CRIES)

828
00:54:56.760 --> 00:55:00.596
Prepare to fight.
If we die, we die with honor.


829
00:55:02.725 --> 00:55:03.975
(YELLING)

830
00:55:13.068 --> 00:55:14.652
(CRIES CONTINUE)

831
00:55:17.781 --> 00:55:20.366
Yao, aim the cannon at Shan
-Yu.

832
00:55:32.212 --> 00:55:33.463
YAO: Hey!

833
00:55:33.797 --> 00:55:35.048
Ping ! Come back!

834
00:55:35.132 --> 00:55:36.466
Ping !

835
00:55:36.717 --> 00:55:37.800
(WHINNIES)

836
00:55:51.482 --> 00:55:53.399
Stop!

837
00:55:59.490 --> 00:56:01.991
All right. You might want
to light that right about now.


838
00:56:02.076 --> 00:56:03.493
Quickly. Quickly!

839
00:56:03.577 --> 00:56:04.660
(FALCON SCREECHING)

840
00:56:05.829 --> 00:56:09.165
Come on ! We gotta help!

841
00:56:17.591 --> 00:56:20.760
MUSHU: You missed !
How could you miss?


842
00:56:20.844 --> 00:56:23.805
It was three feet
in front of you !

843
00:56:32.773 --> 00:56:34.315
(MEN SCREAMING)

844
00:56:37.736 --> 00:56:39.153
(GROWLING)

845
00:56:39.696 --> 00:56:40.863
(GROANING)

846
00:56:49.373 --> 00:56:50.748
(CHEERING)

847
00:56:51.792 --> 00:56:53.584
(ALL THREE EXCLAIMING)

848
00:56:55.129 --> 00:56:56.504
(WHINNYING)

849
00:57:00.843 --> 00:57:02.593
(SCREAMING)

850
00:57:14.148 --> 00:57:15.398
(GASPING)

851
00:57:16.066 --> 00:57:17.400
(YELLING)

852
00:57:26.160 --> 00:57:28.411
MUSHU: Mulan !

853
00:57:31.206 --> 00:57:33.166
Mulan !

854
00:57:33.250 --> 00:57:35.001
-Mulan?
-(GROWLING)


855
00:57:35.085 --> 00:57:37.003
No.

856
00:57:37.087 --> 00:57:39.589
Mulan !

857
00:57:39.673 --> 00:57:42.842
Man, you are one lucky bug.

858
00:57:51.768 --> 00:57:54.770
Shang !

859
00:57:59.943 --> 00:58:03.529
-Do you see them?
-Yes.


860
00:58:06.742 --> 00:58:10.870
Perfect. Now we'll pull
them to safe. . .ty.

861
00:58:13.415 --> 00:58:16.250
Mulan ! I found the lucky cricket!

862
00:58:16.335 --> 00:58:18.419
We need help.

863
00:58:19.546 --> 00:58:24.050
Nice. Very nice. 
You can sit by me.

864
00:58:24.134 --> 00:58:26.844
We're gonna die!

865
00:58:26.929 --> 00:58:28.846
We're gonna die!
We are definitely gonna die.


866
00:58:28.931 --> 00:58:31.974
No way we survive this.
Death is coming !


867
00:58:33.810 --> 00:58:37.855
(BLUBBERING)
I let them slip through my fingers.


868
00:58:37.981 --> 00:58:39.148
(SCREAMING)

869
00:58:39.566 --> 00:58:40.983
(GRUNTING)

870
00:58:41.318 --> 00:58:43.069
Pull !

871
00:58:43.987 --> 00:58:45.279
ALL: Whoa!

872
00:58:46.865 --> 00:58:47.949
Huh !

873
00:58:54.414 --> 00:58:57.375
I knew we could do
it. You the man !

874
00:58:57.459 --> 00:58:59.669
Well, sort of.

875
00:59:03.423 --> 00:59:05.967
LING: Step back, guys.
Give him some air.


876
00:59:06.260 --> 00:59:07.426
(GASPING)

877
00:59:07.511 --> 00:59:08.928
Ping?

878
00:59:09.012 --> 00:59:13.015
You are the craziest man I've ever met.

879
00:59:14.351 --> 00:59:16.894
And for that, I owe you my life.

880
00:59:16.979 --> 00:59:20.439
From now on, you have my trust.

881
00:59:20.524 --> 00:59:24.277
Let's hear it for Ping !
The bravest of us all !


882
00:59:24.361 --> 00:59:26.112
You're king of the mountain !

883
00:59:26.196 --> 00:59:27.947
Yes, yes, yes!

884
00:59:28.031 --> 00:59:29.323
(ALL WHOOPING)

885
00:59:29.408 --> 00:59:30.449
(GROANS)

886
00:59:30.534 --> 00:59:32.660
Ping ! What's wrong?

887
00:59:33.161 --> 00:59:34.495
(GROANING)

888
00:59:36.373 --> 00:59:39.125
He's wounded ! Get help!

889
00:59:40.002 --> 00:59:43.546
Ping, hold on.

890
00:59:44.339 --> 00:59:46.257
Hold on.

891
01:00:01.064 --> 01:00:02.773
(WHISPERING)

892
01:00:15.037 --> 01:00:16.954
(SIGHS) I can explain.

893
01:00:18.040 --> 01:00:20.666
(GASPS) So it's true!

894
01:00:20.751 --> 01:00:22.960
MULAN: Shang !

895
01:00:23.045 --> 01:00:25.963
I knew there was
something wrong with you.


896
01:00:26.048 --> 01:00:27.340
A woman !

897
01:00:27.424 --> 01:00:28.466
(ALL GASPING)

898
01:00:28.550 --> 01:00:31.510
-(GRUNTING)
-Treacherous snake!


899
01:00:31.595 --> 01:00:34.138
My name is Mulan.

900
01:00:34.222 --> 01:00:36.682
I did it to save my father.

901
01:00:36.767 --> 01:00:39.685
-High treason !
-I didn't mean for it to go this far.


902
01:00:39.770 --> 01:00:42.021
Ultimate dishonor!

903
01:00:42.105 --> 01:00:45.816
It was the only way. 
Please believe me.

904
01:00:45.901 --> 01:00:47.943
(SCOFFS) Captain?

905
01:00:54.076 --> 01:00:55.826
-(NEIGHING WILDLY)
-(GASPS)


906
01:00:55.911 --> 01:00:58.329
Restrain him !

907
01:01:00.749 --> 01:01:03.626
-No!
-You know the law.


908
01:01:15.889 --> 01:01:18.307
A life for a life.

909
01:01:18.392 --> 01:01:20.643
My debt is repaid.

910
01:01:22.562 --> 01:01:26.065
-Move out!
-(STUTTERING) But you can't just. . .


911
01:01:26.149 --> 01:01:29.068
I said, "Move out."

912
01:01:53.301 --> 01:01:55.052
(SNORTS)

913
01:01:57.305 --> 01:01:58.848
(NICKERS)

914
01:02:00.809 --> 01:02:02.143
(CHIRPING)

915
01:02:03.311 --> 01:02:04.353
(SHIVERS)

916
01:02:04.438 --> 01:02:06.814
I was this close.

917
01:02:06.898 --> 01:02:10.025
This close to impressin' the ancestors,

918
01:02:10.110 --> 01:02:12.903
gettin' the top shelf, an entourage.

919
01:02:12.988 --> 01:02:16.699
Man. All my fine work. Pfft.

920
01:02:20.495 --> 01:02:22.413
Hi.

921
01:02:22.497 --> 01:02:25.458
I should never have left home.

922
01:02:25.542 --> 01:02:28.836
Hey, come on.
You went to save your father's life.


923
01:02:28.920 --> 01:02:31.464
Who knew you'd end up shamin' him
and disgracing your ancestors


924
01:02:31.548 --> 01:02:34.300
and losin' all your friends?

925
01:02:34.384 --> 01:02:37.636
You know, you just gotta. . .
You gotta learn to let these things go.


926
01:02:37.721 --> 01:02:39.013
(CRYING)

927
01:02:39.890 --> 01:02:42.892
Maybe I didn't go for my father.

928
01:02:42.976 --> 01:02:47.646
Maybe what I really wanted was
to prove I could do things right,


929
01:02:47.731 --> 01:02:51.108
so when I looked in the mirror,

930
01:02:51.193 --> 01:02:53.777
I'd see someone worthwhile.

931
01:02:55.864 --> 01:02:57.990
But I was wrong.

932
01:02:59.367 --> 01:03:01.619
I see nothing.

933
01:03:10.420 --> 01:03:13.672
Now, that's just 'cause
this needs a little spit, that's all.


934
01:03:13.757 --> 01:03:17.259
(SPITS) Let me shine this up for ya.

935
01:03:17.344 --> 01:03:20.429
I can see you.
Look at you. You look so pretty.


936
01:03:25.101 --> 01:03:27.978
The truth is, we're both frauds.

937
01:03:28.063 --> 01:03:31.190
Your ancestors never sent me.
They don't even like me.


938
01:03:31.274 --> 01:03:33.609
I mean, you risked your life
to help people you love.


939
01:03:33.693 --> 01:03:36.028
I risked your life to help myself.

940
01:03:36.112 --> 01:03:38.948
At least you had good intentions.

941
01:03:39.908 --> 01:03:41.617
(SOFT CHIRPING)

942
01:03:42.244 --> 01:03:44.411
What? What do you mean,
"You're not lucky"?


943
01:03:44.496 --> 01:03:47.706
-You lied to me?
-(CHIRPING)


944
01:03:47.791 --> 01:03:50.251
And what are you, a sheep?

945
01:03:50.335 --> 01:03:52.044
-(SNORTS)
-(GRUMBLES)


946
01:03:52.128 --> 01:03:56.215
I'll have to face my father
sooner or later.


947
01:03:56.299 --> 01:03:58.717
Let's go home.

948
01:03:58.802 --> 01:04:02.012
Yeah. This ain't gonna be pretty.

949
01:04:02.097 --> 01:04:05.975
But don't you worry, okay?
Things will work out.


950
01:04:06.059 --> 01:04:10.104
We started this thing together,
and that's how we'll finish it.


951
01:04:11.815 --> 01:04:13.774
I promise.

952
01:04:25.954 --> 01:04:35.954
(SCREECHING)

953
01:04:41.845 --> 01:04:43.178
(GRUNTING)

954
01:04:51.563 --> 01:04:53.022
(YELLING)

955
01:04:55.942 --> 01:04:57.860
(YELLING ECHOES)

956
01:05:00.614 --> 01:05:02.031
(GRUNTING)

957
01:05:05.035 --> 01:05:06.785
(BOTH GRUNTING)

958
01:05:07.287 --> 01:05:08.662
(GROWLING)

959
01:05:30.477 --> 01:05:31.852
(GASPS)

960
01:05:36.399 --> 01:05:38.525
Uh, home is that way.

961
01:05:38.610 --> 01:05:41.862
-I have to do something.
-Did you see those Huns?


962
01:05:41.946 --> 01:05:44.907
They popped out of the snow. . .
Like daisies!


963
01:05:44.991 --> 01:05:48.077
Are we in this together or not?

964
01:05:50.163 --> 01:05:51.497
(CHIRPING)

965
01:05:51.581 --> 01:05:55.125
Well, let's go kick some Hunny buns!

966
01:05:55.210 --> 01:05:57.127
Yee-haw!

967
01:05:57.212 --> 01:05:58.545
(WHOOPING)

968
01:06:02.384 --> 01:06:04.259
(TRADITIONAL MUSIC PLAYING)

969
01:06:06.763 --> 01:06:08.430
(CROWD CHEERING)

970
01:06:16.523 --> 01:06:20.234
Make way for the heroes of China.

971
01:06:28.576 --> 01:06:30.369
(WOMAN CRIES OUT)

972
01:06:34.582 --> 01:06:36.917
-Shang !
-Mulan?


973
01:06:37.001 --> 01:06:39.420
The Huns are alive! 
They're in the city!

974
01:06:39.504 --> 01:06:42.172
You don't belong here, Mulan. Go home.

975
01:06:44.926 --> 01:06:48.929
Shang, I saw them in the mountains.
You have to believe me.


976
01:06:49.013 --> 01:06:50.514
Why should I?

977
01:06:53.893 --> 01:06:56.770
Why else would I come back?

978
01:06:56.855 --> 01:07:01.650
You said you'd trust Ping.
Why is Mulan any different?


979
01:07:09.117 --> 01:07:13.662
Keep your eyes open.
I know they're here.


980
01:07:19.878 --> 01:07:21.587
(CROWD CHEERING)

981
01:07:22.213 --> 01:07:23.964
Now, where are you going?

982
01:07:24.048 --> 01:07:26.675
To find someone who will believe me.

983
01:07:57.582 --> 01:08:01.502
My children, heaven smiles down

984
01:08:01.586 --> 01:08:03.754
upon the Middle Kingdom.

985
01:08:03.838 --> 01:08:07.466
China will sleep safely tonight.

986
01:08:07.550 --> 01:08:10.344
Thanks to our brave warriors.

987
01:08:10.428 --> 01:08:12.346
(CROWD CHEERING)

988
01:08:12.430 --> 01:08:14.640
Sir, the Emperor's in danger.

989
01:08:14.724 --> 01:08:15.808
(HARRUMPHS)

990
01:08:15.892 --> 01:08:18.060
But the Huns are here.

991
01:08:18.144 --> 01:08:21.021
-Please, you have to help.
-(HARRUMPHS)


992
01:08:22.899 --> 01:08:24.483
No one will listen.

993
01:08:24.567 --> 01:08:26.318
Huh? Oh, I'm sorry.
Did you say something?


994
01:08:26.402 --> 01:08:30.364
-Mushu.
-You're a girl again, remember?


995
01:08:30.448 --> 01:08:35.953
Your Majesty, I present to you
the sword of Shan-Yu.


996
01:08:36.037 --> 01:08:39.498
I know what this means
to you, Captain Li.


997
01:08:39.582 --> 01:08:43.168
Your father would have been
very proud.


998
01:08:43.378 --> 01:08:44.753
(SCREECHING)

999
01:08:47.382 --> 01:08:48.632
(ALL GASPING)

1000
01:08:54.848 --> 01:08:56.557
-(PEOPLE SCREAMING)
-(GASPING)


1001
01:08:59.602 --> 01:09:01.019
(SCREECHING)

1002
01:09:01.688 --> 01:09:03.146
(GROWLING)

1003
01:09:10.154 --> 01:09:13.198
-No!
-Come on !


1004
01:09:17.328 --> 01:09:19.246
(CACKLING)

1005
01:09:20.874 --> 01:09:22.457
(GRUNTING)

1006
01:09:30.383 --> 01:09:32.968
They'll never reach the Emperor in time.

1007
01:09:33.052 --> 01:09:34.845
(BATTERING CONTINUES)

1008
01:09:37.599 --> 01:09:39.224
(WHISTLING) Hey, guys!

1009
01:09:39.309 --> 01:09:41.727
I've got an idea.

1010
01:09:54.824 --> 01:09:57.534
(SINGING)
Be a man


1011
01:09:57.619 --> 01:10:01.830
-We must be swift as a coursing river
-Be a man


1012
01:10:01.915 --> 01:10:05.417
-With all the force of a great typhoon
-Be a man


1013
01:10:05.501 --> 01:10:09.087
With all the strength of a raging fire

1014
01:10:09.172 --> 01:10:13.926
Mysterious as the dark side
of the moon


1015
01:10:21.142 --> 01:10:24.019
(PEOPLE EXCLAIMING)

1016
01:10:26.439 --> 01:10:27.439
Boo.

1017
01:10:29.275 --> 01:10:30.651
